name: Daily Average Flow
query:
select 
Project, Customer  , biox_wier_notch_type As "Structure Type", 
date(measurement_date) as "Measurement Date:Date:100", avg(flow_volume) as "Daily Volume (Avg MLD):Float:100"
from `tabOnsite Flow Measurement`
group by date(measurement_date), Project, Customer, biox_wier_notch_type
order by Project, Customer, measurement_date
